553
00:42:53,821 --> 00:42:54,821
Look at me.

554
00:42:54,864 --> 00:42:56,821
Focus on my voice.

555
00:42:56,908 --> 00:42:58,945
We're going to get
through this together.

556
00:42:59,035 --> 00:43:00,901
