612
00:48:08,677 --> 00:48:10,155
You pushed down
all that pain and anger...

613
00:48:10,179 --> 00:48:11,490
- Jean?
- ...where do you think it's gonna go?

614
00:48:11,514 --> 00:48:12,971
I did that to help her.
What I do,

615
