645
00:50:47,086 --> 00:50:48,122
Um...

646
00:50:50,297 --> 00:50:51,583
Maybe, uh...

647
00:50:53,259 --> 00:50:56,627
it might be better
if I talk to a lawyer.

648
00:51:00,558 --> 00:51:02,595
