come here to ask me?

673
00:53:42,344 --> 00:53:44,882
How did you stop?

674
00:53:51,937 --> 00:53:54,270
I've lived with vengeance
my whole life.

675
00:53:55,774 --> 00:53:58,141
Ever since I was a child, I...

676
00:53:58,819 --> 00:54:01,732
